            "title": "晶圓祭出「氦氣」保衛戰？經濟部攜手3大氣體商緊急盤點 供應穩定無虞",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E7iDealOwSSMylOg1A5r.w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/c82911064905def72c439a08f2b85bab\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
